Package: aegis-siem-server
Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-pip, postgresql (>= 12), nginx, systemd
Maintainer: Mokshit Bindal <mokshit@aegis-siem.dev>
Description: Aegis SIEM Server - Enterprise Security Monitoring
 Aegis SIEM is a comprehensive security information and event management
 system with ML-based anomaly detection, real-time monitoring, and
 centralized security event management.
 .
 This package installs the Aegis SIEM server with:
  - FastAPI backend with REST API
  - PostgreSQL database integration
  - ML-based anomaly detection
  - Alert management and triage
  - Role-based access control (RBAC)
  - Process monitoring
  - React-based dashboard
  - Nginx reverse proxy configuration
Homepage: https://github.com/MokshitBindal/Aegis
